---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import HubSpotForm from '../../components/HubSpotForm.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Contact Us | Consilegy"
  description="Tell us about your Japan or APAC revenue operations challenge. We work with English-speaking leaders in Japan and APAC who need their CRM, RevOps, and GTM to actually work for how Japan moves."
  lang="en"
>
  <div class="contact-en">

    <div class="contact-en__hero">
      <h1 class="contact-en__heading">Contact Us</h1>
      <p class="contact-en__lead">
        Tell us where you are: what you're managing, where execution is breaking,
        and what you're trying to solve. We'll be direct about whether and how we can help.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-en__topics">
      <p class="contact-en__topics-label">Common situations we help with:</p>
      <ul class="contact-en__topics-list">
        <li>CRM that doesn't reflect Japan pipeline reality</li>
        <li>Japan revenue you can't fully see inside from the EN side</li>
        <li>Messaging and conversion paths that don't work for Japan buyers</li>
        <li>Revenue architecture and funnel design for Japan operations</li>
        <li>HubSpot or Salesforce implementation for Japan-facing teams</li>
        <li>Taking ownership of Japan or APAC revenue for the first time</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-en__form">
      <HubSpotForm
        portalId="46498743"
        formId="29d27c94-87f9-453f-a21d-8ef585b53364"
      />
    </div>

    <p class="contact-en__note">
      We usually respond with the most appropriate next step based on your situation, scope, and timing.
    </p>

  </div>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .contact-en {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-md) var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .contact-en__hero {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .contact-en__heading {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
  }

  .contact-en__lead {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .contact-en__topics {
    background: #f8f9fc;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .contact-en__topics-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .contact-en__topics-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.4rem 2rem;
  }

  .contact-en__topics-list li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .contact-en__topics-list li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .contact-en__form {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .contact-en__note {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .contact-en__topics-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
